{
  "stem": "18960.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they-- they knew we were-- I was coming.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They came out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They wanted to find out from me what's going on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I still managed, before I left, to get a-- a blank form of a birth certificate.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "A Polish certificate.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the brother-in-law of a doctor-- of my cousin Naftali Backenroth, he was a doctor.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He was a medical doctor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Dr.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Szmer.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was one-- he was hiding there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I told him I-- he should fill out my birth certificate, because I had no paper, no documents whatsoever, besides this-- the document I'm going to have.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we filled it out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We decided the name-- what kind of a name to fill out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "A name should sound either Polish or Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We decided on the name Stefan [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Galuska. ?] He fill it out as-- with his handwriting.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "That was my only document I had, which was, of course, not sufficient.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And the next-- I slept over that night.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And the next night, we-- we went to a next village, where was a railroad station.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Small village.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And that's-- that railroad was heading towards Lwow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] the transport of those workers from-- was going from Lwow to Germany.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I was supposed to go with the train to Lwow at night.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Dark at night.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It was maybe 1 o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I can't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And this guy, the actual guy that came for-- for that so-called Urlaub, he was-- accompanied me to Lwow.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "When we came to Lwow, it was daylight already.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And there was an Aktion going in-- in process.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I saw they were-- they were hurting Jews on the street.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And-- and-- but there was a big camp in Lwow called Janowska.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
